{"content": "I need to multiply 322\u2089 \u00d7 352\u2089.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n322\u2089 = 3\u00d79\u00b2 + 2\u00d79\u00b9 + 2\u00d79\u2070 = 3\u00d781 + 2\u00d79 + 2\u00d71 = 243 + 18 + 2 = 263\u2081\u2080\n\n352\u2089 = 3\u00d79\u00b2 + 5\u00d79\u00b9 + 2\u00d79\u2070 = 3\u00d781 + 5\u00d79 + 2\u00d71 = 243 + 45 + 2 = 290\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n\n263 \u00d7 290 = 76,270\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n\n76270 \u00f7 9 = 8474 r 4\n8474 \u00f7 9 = 941 r 5\n941 \u00f7 9 = 104 r 5\n104 \u00f7 9 = 11 r 5\n11 \u00f7 9 = 1 r 2\n1 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 1\n\nReading from bottom to top: **125554\u2089**\n\n**Verification:**\n125554\u2089 = 1\u00d759049 + 2\u00d76561 + 5\u00d7729 + 5\u00d781 + 5\u00d79 + 4\u00d71 = 59049 + 13122 + 3645 + 405 + 45 + 4 = 76270\u2081\u2080 \u2713\n\n125554", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 1150, "completion_tokens": 411}